<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>重置密码</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
        }
        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .logo {
            padding: 32px 40px 24px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        }
        .logo svg {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 24px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #525252;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 11px 24px;
            background: #171717;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .link {
            margin: 16px 0;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #737373;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        .expires {
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #fef3c7;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 24px 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #a3a3a3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">
                <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <defs>
                        <linearGradient id="bgGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                            <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#6a5fc1;stop-opacity:1" />
                            <stop offset="50%" style="stop-color:#8c5393;stop-opacity:1" />
                            <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#e1567c;stop-opacity:1" />
                        </linearGradient>
                    </defs>
                    <rect x="20" y="20" width="160" height="160" rx="24" fill="url(#bgGradient)"/>
                    <g transform="rotate(30 100 100)">
                        <path d="M 55 95 Q 100 50 145 95" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.3"/>
                        <path d="M 68 108 Q 100 76 132 108" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.5"/>
                        <path d="M 81 121 Q 100 102 119 121" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.7"/>
                    </g>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h1>重置密码</h1>
                <p>收到了你的密码重置请求,点击下面的按钮重置密码:</p>

                <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">重置密码</a>

                <p>或者复制链接到浏览器:</p>
                <div class="link">{{resetUrl}}</div>

                <div class="expires">链接 {{expiresIn}} 小时后失效</div>

                <p>如果不是你本人操作,忽略这封邮件即可。</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                Sky Monitor · 2025
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

